, 
<figureCitation id="130B58A1FFCBDB77B312417B9C5A9673" box="[262,290,1034,1060]" captionStart="FIGURE 27" captionStartId="12.[151,250,1591,1615]" captionTargetBox="[159,1428,926,1563]" captionTargetId="figure-316@12.[155,1432,921,1568]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURE 27. Distribution of Saropogon species in Russia, Transcaucasia and Central Asia (based on the available material and Abbassian-Lintzen 1964, Richter 1968, Mohammadi et al. 2017)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4414405" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4414405/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="581">27</figureCitation>
